    </JadeMethod>
    <JadeMethod name="createWOJobSheet" id="b28ad8a5-8bb8-4c70-9b52-d74323e76563">
        <source>createWOJobSheet(_controller: CnEcReleaseController);
/*

Purpose:			
This will be used to add single work order job sheet for each terminal
Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
12 May 2023	navma1	ChangeRequest 57932:[54556] EUP - Delivery Dispatch [Framework] Required

*/

